section.section:
A person to whom a parking placard for a person with a disability is issued shall display the placard described in this section:
In a Class A (passenger) vehicle or a Class M (multipurpose) vehicle;
On a Class D (motorcycle) vehicle as required by the Administration;
In a Class E (truck) vehicle with a one ton or less manufacturer's rated capacity and specially equipped for the transportation of or operation by an individual with a disability; or
In a Class H, I, or J vehicle that is specially equipped for the transportation of individuals with disabilities and is used exclusively for the transportation of individuals with disabilities.
